== Adjective ==

# In birds: A [[hen]] that sits tightly and protectively on a [[nest]], in order to hatch [[egg]]s (eg, 'a broody hen').
# In general: Any creature or person interested in raising [[young]].

=== Synonyms ===

The word ''clucky'' is often used interchangably with ''broody''.  Broody hens usually [[cluck]] loudly and continuously if disturbed.